author: taylor
msg: New method added to Profiler interface: createProfile( ProfileLocator locator, Portlets portlets)
This method supports creating new profiles without cloning another profile.
You can pass in a PSML tree constructed in memory in the second 'portlets' parameter, and the locator is used to specify the location of the psml resource.
